{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="legal-section">
    <div class="container legal-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
      <h1>Website Terms</h1>
      <p>This site is a demonstration website for {{ site.businessName }}. The names, artwork, contact details, and publication plans shown here are placeholders for concept review unless and until the real project is launched.</p>
      <p>Nothing on this placeholder site should be treated as an official diocesan statement, formal pastoral direction, binding service offer, or final publication schedule. Confirm all real-world details directly before relying on them.</p>
      <p>All public wording, images, and contact details can be updated through the local editor and rebuilt into static output. Replace these terms before taking payments, processing donations, collecting subscribers, or publishing under a final legal entity.</p>
      <p>Use the published contact details for questions about collaboration, launch planning, or the current placeholder concept.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
